00:14:04,690 --> 00:14:06,780
Moria!

1137
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:09,950
Don't you like...

1138
00:14:09,950 --> 00:14:12,240
to party?!

1139
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:33,720
Did you read the morning paper?

1140
00:14:35,520 --> 00:14:38,060
There's never a dull moment!

1141
00:14:39,310 --> 00:14:42,270
On the fourth day of the Reverie...

1142
00:14:42,270 --> 00:14:44,980
the commanders of the Revolutionary Army...

1143
00:14:44,980 --> 00:14:49,860
burst into the Sacred Mary
Geoise to take back Kuma,

1144
00:14:49,860 --> 00:14:56,200
and clashed with Marine Admirals
Ryokugyu and Fujitora!

1145
00:14:58,500 --> 00:15:00,790
Meanwhile...

1146
00:15:01,420 --> 00:15:05,380
in Wano where the monstrous Kaido resides...

1147
00:15:06,170 --> 00:15:08,590
the arrival of Straw Hat...

1148
00:15:08,630 --> 00:15:12,090
and a bunch of other hot-blooded
punks has made headlines.

1149
00:15:12,890 --> 00:15:15,310
And chasing them is...

1150
00:15:15,310 --> 00:15:20,020
the mad Emperor Big Mom!

1151
00:15:24,900 --> 00:15:26,610
What do you think will happen?!

1152
00:15:33,160 --> 00:15:36,160
It's already begun.

1153
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:38,790
In order to sit on the throne...

1154
00:15:38,790 --> 00:15:43,290
the mighty will crush one another!

