1224
00:18:06,350 --> 00:18:08,560
He's as strong as Duke Inuarashi!

1225
00:18:08,560 --> 00:18:12,860
That he can give Duke Inuarashi a run
for his money... How impressive...

1226
00:18:13,440 --> 00:18:15,410
Why, Ashura?

1227
00:18:15,410 --> 00:18:21,530
Why not use that tremendous power
for Kuri, for Lord Oden's beloved people?!

1228
00:18:30,630 --> 00:18:33,210
He's dead!

1229
00:18:33,210 --> 00:18:37,420
Why did you guys even bother
coming back after all this time?!

1230
00:18:37,420 --> 00:18:40,720
We came back to fulfill Lord Oden's dream!

1231
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:45,350
But you-gara have forgotten
what happened to Lord Oden

1232
00:18:45,350 --> 00:18:48,060
and are doing as you please with your sword!

1233
00:18:48,060 --> 00:18:49,690
Shut up!

1234
00:18:58,440 --> 00:19:02,280
Don't talk as if you know everything!

1235
00:19:02,910 --> 00:19:05,990
If there is something you
want to say, then say it!

1236
00:19:11,250 --> 00:19:14,540
Foxfire Style: Fire-Willow Flash!

1237
00:19:24,600 --> 00:19:25,850
Gentlemen...

1238
00:19:27,770 --> 00:19:29,810
That's enough.

1239
00:19:31,060 --> 00:19:32,100
Inuarashi!

1240
00:19:32,810 --> 00:19:33,860
Ashura!

1241
00:19:42,360 --> 00:19:45,070
I thought you were better than this, Ashura!

1242
00:19:47,740 --> 00:19:49,200
Kiku!

1243
00:19:49,620 --> 00:19:55,500
I've watched Wano since
Lord Oden died two decades ago.

1244
00:19:55,500 --> 00:20:00,420
You all think you can
show up now and preach to me?

1245
00:20:00,420 --> 00:20:01,380
I won't listen!

1246
00:20:04,970 --> 00:20:09,970
You should be thankful I'm not
robbing you blind before I go!

1247
00:20:10,520 --> 00:20:12,020
Don't you remember?!

1248
00:20:12,440 --> 00:20:15,650
This is how we were even back then!

1249
00:20:16,560 --> 00:20:21,320
I was fascinated by that man, Kozuki Oden.

1250
00:20:21,320 --> 00:20:26,120
I risked my life for him as a samurai!

1251
00:20:26,120 --> 00:20:30,910
But I never pledged to support
the rest of the Kozuki clan!

1252
00:20:33,210 --> 00:20:34,080
Right...

1253
00:20:35,380 --> 00:20:37,090
Momonosuke?

1254
00:20:48,760 --> 00:20:53,940
Then I suggest you remember
the kind of man that I was!

1255
00:20:55,060 --> 00:20:57,020
I won't give up!

1256
00:20:58,060 --> 00:20:59,770
I'll have you join us!

1257
00:21:01,730 --> 00:21:08,200
Don't assume that everyone will be thrilled
to see the return of the Kozuki Clan's samurai!

1258
00:21:11,870 --> 00:21:17,000
You guys abandoned the country
for twenty years!

1259
00:21:17,750 --> 00:21:20,340
You will never make up for that lost time!

1260
00:21:30,720 --> 00:21:32,520
Are you hurt?

1261
00:21:32,520 --> 00:21:33,680
No.

1262
00:21:34,480 --> 00:21:35,350
Let's go.

1263
00:21:38,060 --> 00:21:40,020
I am sorry to interrupt you.

1264
00:21:40,020 --> 00:21:41,020
Raizo...!

1265
00:21:41,020 --> 00:21:44,530
I was able to locate Sir Luffy.

1266
00:21:44,530 --> 00:21:47,700
He is at the prisoner mining camp in Udon.

1267
00:21:47,700 --> 00:21:52,200
I thought so! Then, I am
counting on you to handle it.

1268
00:21:52,200 --> 00:21:53,540
Understood!

1269
00:22:00,880 --> 00:22:03,000
Otama! Are you awake?!

1270
00:22:05,510 --> 00:22:09,260
Master, what happened to me?

1271
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:15,930
You were attacked by Kaido,
but these people treated you!

1272
00:22:17,560 --> 00:22:19,600
Oh, I see.

1273
00:22:19,600 --> 00:22:21,560
Thank you!

1274
00:22:21,560 --> 00:22:23,190
I am grateful!

1275
00:22:23,190 --> 00:22:26,690
Your injuries were minor.
You'll get better soon!

1276
00:22:26,690 --> 00:22:28,490
Thanks!

1277
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:36,500
I was so scared, I just passed out.

1278
00:22:36,500 --> 00:22:41,880
I don't really remember the attack.

1279
00:22:42,420 --> 00:22:46,210
I kinda remember Horsella fighting real hard...

1280
00:22:48,720 --> 00:22:50,930
Where to, Master?!

1281
00:22:56,020 --> 00:22:59,940
An enemy became that loyal to you?

1282
00:22:59,940 --> 00:23:01,600
What an astonishing power!

1283
00:23:01,600 --> 00:23:05,150
What happened to Horsella
and Big Bro?! Are they okay?!

1284
00:23:06,030 --> 00:23:09,110
We don't know what happened to Horsella...

1285
00:23:10,320 --> 00:23:11,530
But Luffy was...

1286
00:23:19,910 --> 00:23:20,790
What?!

1287
00:23:21,370 --> 00:23:24,000
Big Bro was pretty badly hurt...

1288
00:23:24,420 --> 00:23:26,550
and taken to the mine in Udon?!

1289
00:23:27,420 --> 00:23:28,800
Oh no!

1290
00:23:28,800 --> 00:23:30,510
Hey, you're wounded!

1291
00:23:30,510 --> 00:23:34,890
I'm more worried about
Big Bro Luffy than my wounds!

1292
00:23:34,890 --> 00:23:39,270
He'll be fine! Luffy's our captain!

1293
00:23:41,100 --> 00:23:44,610
Udon is a region of Wano.

1294
00:23:44,610 --> 00:23:50,240
These days, it is mostly known
for the prisoner mining camp.

1295
00:23:51,030 --> 00:23:57,620
Udon, Wano

1296
00:23:51,530 --> 00:23:55,700
It's a dreadful place where serious offenders

1297
00:23:55,700 --> 00:23:59,360
are forced to perform hard labor until they die.

1298
00:23:59,360 --> 00:24:01,290
No one has ever escaped.

1299
00:24:16,890 --> 00:24:19,310
No, we don't need any geisha.

1300
00:24:19,310 --> 00:24:22,310
Don't let anyone near this room!

1301
00:24:22,310 --> 00:24:23,350
Yes, sir!

1302
00:24:44,670 --> 00:24:48,380
You're bad...!

1303
00:24:54,510 --> 00:24:58,930
Here's the order for armor and weapons.

1304
00:24:58,930 --> 00:25:01,680
You're definitely bad!

1305
00:25:02,980 --> 00:25:04,560
Huh? Am I?

1306
00:25:04,980 --> 00:25:09,690
Oh, this is a lot! Is there
going to be a war or something?

1307
00:25:09,690 --> 00:25:12,280
We don't know what's happening abroad.

1308
00:25:12,280 --> 00:25:15,240
We just make whatever they want.

1309
00:25:15,240 --> 00:25:18,280
You're so, so bad!

1310
00:25:20,160 --> 00:25:21,410
Huh? Am I?

1311
00:25:21,410 --> 00:25:25,080
Look closely, Onami.
My old eyes can't handle this.

1312
00:25:25,540 --> 00:25:28,460
You're doing great!
Keep calm while you watch.

1313
00:25:29,750 --> 00:25:31,630
His head is blocking my view.

1314
00:25:33,840 --> 00:25:35,090
Somebody's there!

1315
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:36,470
Who is it?!

1316
00:25:47,440 --> 00:25:48,440
Who are they?!

1317
00:25:52,400 --> 00:25:53,990
Search the attic!

1318
00:25:53,990 --> 00:25:56,030
Catch them at any cost!

1319
00:25:57,910 --> 00:26:00,280
Calm down, Shinobu!

1320
00:26:00,280 --> 00:26:01,620
You're not getting away!

1321
00:26:10,250 --> 00:26:11,920
Be quiet!

1322
00:26:12,750 --> 00:26:14,340
Where did they go?!

1323
00:26:19,970 --> 00:26:22,100
Oh, is it just a cat?

1324
00:27:02,220 --> 00:27:03,760
Where'd they go?!

1325
00:27:14,900 --> 00:27:17,360
What's the matter with you, Shinobu?!

1326
00:27:22,700 --> 00:27:23,910
