1633
00:31:35,870 --> 00:31:38,660
Now, gather 'round! Gather 'round!

1634
00:31:38,660 --> 00:31:44,080
There's also news about the Witching Hour Boy,
who appears at the third hour after midnight!

1635
00:31:44,080 --> 00:31:46,300
He's a thief who steals from the rich...

1636
00:31:46,300 --> 00:31:50,220
and gives to the poor living
in tenement houses!

1637
00:31:50,220 --> 00:31:53,550
Is he a hero or a villain?!

1638
00:31:53,550 --> 00:31:56,220
What is his true identity?!

1639
00:31:56,220 --> 00:31:59,270
If you want to know, buy a notice paper!

1640
00:31:59,270 --> 00:32:01,520
Ah! Sir Witching Hour!

1641
00:32:01,520 --> 00:32:02,900
I'll take one!

1642
00:32:02,900 --> 00:32:04,020
Yes, thank you!

1643
00:32:04,020 --> 00:32:05,650
Come and get your own!

1644
00:32:05,650 --> 00:32:08,610
This notice paper is filled with exclusives!

1645
00:32:08,610 --> 00:32:10,450
I'll take one, too!

1646
00:32:10,450 --> 00:32:11,570
Me, too!

1647
00:32:25,710 --> 00:32:27,460
The reversed crescent moon!

1648
00:32:30,800 --> 00:32:31,880
Who gave me this?

1649
00:33:17,050 --> 00:33:19,510
Are they really back?!

1650
00:33:28,770 --> 00:33:30,520
– The Kozuki Clan!
– The Kozuki Clan!

1651
00:33:40,530 --> 00:33:43,870
Hey, this could be the work of those ghosts.

1652
00:33:43,870 --> 00:33:47,210
Suspicion will get us nowhere!
This will spark a great fire!

1653
00:33:50,420 --> 00:33:51,800
I'm going!

1654
00:33:53,550 --> 00:33:58,300
If this were ten years ago,
I would have fought...

1655
00:33:59,140 --> 00:34:02,390
But what are you all going to do for weapons?

1656
00:34:03,930 --> 00:34:07,770
This country prohibits all but samurai
from carrying weapons.

1657
00:34:09,100 --> 00:34:11,360
All the kendo halls have closed down.

1658
00:34:11,360 --> 00:34:16,030
Martial arts like karate
and judo are also prohibited.

1659
00:34:16,030 --> 00:34:19,490
Orochi has already stamped out
the spark of rebellion.

1660
00:34:20,280 --> 00:34:23,040
I'll fight even if it's with my bare hands!

1661
00:34:23,040 --> 00:34:27,500
This will be our last chance!
I've been waiting for so long!

1662
00:34:27,500 --> 00:34:28,920
I can't stop...

1663
00:34:29,630 --> 00:34:31,790
trembling with excitement!

1664
00:34:31,790 --> 00:34:39,220
Udon Prison Mine
Wano

1665
00:35:02,200 --> 00:35:03,080
Sir Luffy.

1666
00:35:03,080 --> 00:35:04,700
Raizo!

1667
00:35:05,200 --> 00:35:06,750
Not so loud!

1668
00:35:08,790 --> 00:35:09,830
What's wrong?

1669
00:35:10,710 --> 00:35:14,130
Nothing. I actually have good news.

1670
00:35:14,840 --> 00:35:16,960
Otama is better.

1671
00:35:17,670 --> 00:35:19,880
Oh! She is?!

1672
00:35:28,020 --> 00:35:29,560
Okay, I'll be back later.

1673
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:30,440
Okay.

1674
00:35:31,230 --> 00:35:33,480
Ya-hoo!

1675
00:35:45,030 --> 00:35:46,080
Hey, Jack...

1676
00:35:47,200 --> 00:35:49,290
the revenue from Kuri is pathetic.

1677
00:35:56,040 --> 00:35:57,880
Now that Doflamingo's not around...

1678
00:35:58,340 --> 00:36:02,090
you know who our next business
partner is, don't you?!

1679
00:36:02,590 --> 00:36:04,970
I'm sorry, Brothers...

1680
00:36:10,020 --> 00:36:13,600
We don't need more deadweight
than this idiot Queen.

1681
00:36:14,400 --> 00:36:19,070
That's right! You don't need
more scum when you've got King.

1682
00:36:22,570 --> 00:36:27,330
Queen "the Plague"
Superstar
Beast Pirates

1683
00:36:22,570 --> 00:36:27,330
King "the Wildfire"
Superstar
Beast Pirates

1684
00:36:24,320 --> 00:36:27,330
– Got that, Jack the stooge?!
– Got that, Jack the stooge?!

1685
00:36:30,950 --> 00:36:33,210
And you, Queen!

1686
00:36:34,120 --> 00:36:39,800
Why is it taking so long to break those brats?!

1687
00:36:39,800 --> 00:36:41,260
You no-account bum!

1688
00:36:41,260 --> 00:36:44,970
Shut it, you sadistic pervert!
